Question 4

summary_nfl_sal <- nfl_sal_tidy %>% 
  group_by(position, year) %>% 
  summarize(salary= mean(salary, na.rm = TRUE))
`summarise()` has grouped output by 'position'. You can override using the
`.groups` argument.
